==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cycadopsida
<hw>Cycadopsida</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a class or subdivision of
plants comprising palmlike gymnosperms: it includes the surviving order
<ord>Cycadales</ord> and several extinct orders; possibly not a natural
group; in some systems considered a class (<class>Cycadopsida</class>)
and in others a subdivision (Cycadophytina or Cycadophyta).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> class Cycadopsida, subdivision Cycadophytina,
subdivision Cycadophyta.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

